  "prompt": "How long HCL technology takes to give offer letter after document uploading round for experience?",
  "response": "The timeline for receiving an offer letter from HCL Technologies after the document uploading round can vary based on several factors, including the specific recruitment process, the number of candidates being processed, and the urgency of hiring for the role. Generally, candidates may receive an offer letter within a few days to a few weeks after the final interview and document verification stages are completed. \n\nTo get the most accurate information, it's best to directly communicate with the HR representative handling your application or refer to any official communications you've received from HCL.",
